NAME
    Test::ProveRdeps - Test using App::ProveRdeps

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of Test::ProveRdeps (from Perl
    distribution Test-ProveRdeps), released on 2020-01-30.

SYNOPSIS
     use Test::ProveRdeps tests=>1;
     all_rdeps_ok(
         modules => ["Foo::Bar"],
         # other options will be passed to App::ProveRdeps::prove_rdeps()
     );

DESCRIPTION
    EXPERIMENTAL.

FUNCTIONS
  all_rdeps_ok
HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Test-ProveRdeps>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Test-ProveDeps>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Test-ProveRdeps>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

SEE ALSO
    App::ProveRdeps and prove-rdeps.

